snippet.title: DRAGON BALL Z: KAKAROT – The 23rd World Tournament Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
DRAGON BALL Z: KAKAROT has more in store for its fans starting today: 
 
Join Goku in his legendary battle at the 23rd World Martial Arts Tournament.
Strike your way through your opponents or knock them out of the ring to become victorious!
 
DLC 5 available on August 17, 2023! #DBZK
 
🥊http://bnent.eu/BuyDBZK
